# Worker task: adversarially verify the freshness scheduling and alerts

You are an adversarial verifier on [Typesense Reboot Recovery](../projects/typesense-reboot-recovery/typesense-reboot-recovery-brief.svx). A worker built and closed [Keep the Critical DB Fresh](../projects/typesense-reboot-recovery/keep-critical-db-fresh.svx) — read its Result. Uncommitted changes live in `packages/system-bus/**` (scheduled rebuild function + staleness alerts) and possibly new `scripts/export-*`. Note: steering has since fixed the five malformed observer pages (dark-wizard `362e662`) and proven a live builder publish. Try to refute the claim that `critical.db` cannot silently rot.

