5. Regression sweep: the 12 fixture tests, `bunx tsc --noEmit`, targeted Biome; registrations coexist with the message-event hunks.

Containment: fixtures only — no real alert sends, no production Redis keys, no Typesense mutations, `~/.joelclaw/runs-dev` read-only, never modify `critical.db` outside the builder's own path, do not restart the worker, do not commit.

